Package com.quackology.duckdevices.spaces

Class MatComplex

java.lang.Object
com.quackology.duckdevices.spaces.MatComplex
All Implemented Interfaces:
Linear, Mat<MatComplex>, Space
public class MatComplex extends Object implements Mat<MatComplex>
Wrapper class for 2D matrix of complex numbers

Based on OjAlgo's ComplexMatrix interface (MatrixC128)
